text: Eva Maria Joann Janssens (born 16 July 1996) is a German badminton player. In 2015, she won gold and bronze medals at the European Junior Badminton Championships in mixed & girls' doubles events. == Achievements == === European Junior Championships === Girls' doubles {| class="sortable wikitable" style="font-size: 90%;" !
